    "elements": [
        {
            "type": "h1",
            "content": "Arabic & Mixed BIDI Layout Tests"
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "content": "This fixture specifically tests the visual accuracy, fontkit shaping integration, and Unicode Bidi Algorithm implementation for complex RTL scripts."
        },
        {
            "type": "h2",
            "content": "1. Pure Arabic Shaping (RTL Mode)"
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "properties": {
                "style": {
                    "direction": "rtl",
                    "fontFamily": "Noto Sans Arabic",
                    "fontSize": 36,
                    "lineHeight": 1.5,
                    "marginBottom": 24
                }
            },
            "content": "مرحبا بك في عالم الطباعة المبرمجة."
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "content": "Notice how the letters connect smoothly. This confirms fontkit is receiving the 'arab' script tag and 'rtl' direction correctly."
        },
        {
            "type": "h2",
            "content": "2. Mixed Script - Arabic inside English (LTR Base)"
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "properties": {
                "style": {
                    "fontSize": 36,
                    "lineHeight": 1.5,
                    "marginBottom": 24
                }
            },
            "content": "The word للنشر means 'for publishing' and مرحباً means 'welcome' in Arabic."
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "content": "The Arabic words should be shaped correctly, written right-to-left internally, but the overall sentence flows left-to-right."
        },
        {
            "type": "h2",
            "content": "3. Mixed Script - English inside Arabic (RTL Base)"
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "properties": {
                "style": {
                    "direction": "rtl",
                    "fontSize": 36,
                    "lineHeight": 1.5,
                    "marginBottom": 24
                }
            },
            "content": "تم تصميم VMPrint 0.1.0 لإنتاج مستندات PDF بدقة متناهية."
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "content": "The base paragraph direction is RTL. The English product name 'VMPrint 0.1.0' should flow LTR within the RTL stream."
        },
        {
            "type": "h2",
            "content": "4. Arabic Punctuation and Numbers"
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "properties": {
                "style": {
                    "direction": "rtl",
                    "fontFamily": "Noto Sans Arabic",
                    "fontSize": 36,
                    "lineHeight": 1.5,
                    "marginBottom": 24
                }
            },
            "content": "تتطلب نسبة 100% من المشاريع دقة في الأرقام (مثل 123,456) وعلامات الترقيم؟ نعم، بالتأكيد!"
        },
        {
            "type": "p",
            "content": "The numbers '100%' and '123,456' must be ordered correctly despite being nested in RTL context."
        }
    ]
}